{
 "name": "RPlog_Out_of_the_Sewer_Into_the_Fire",
 "title": "Out of the Sewer, Into the Fire",
 "summary": "In Fountain Square in Plaxton City, the hunted dark adept Simon Sezirok and his eccentric companion Mira find themselves caught up in a tense confrontation involving the guard Collier and a developing distraction. When guards' blasters swing dangerously toward Mira, Simon flicks his hand and uses the Force to knock the weapons from their grasp. Seizing the moment, Simon hauls Mira to her feet and the pair flee the square, escaping one peril only to plunge toward the next.",
